QuestData.Title: Knock 'Em Out The Box
QuestData.Description:
Steelarm Pillagers have been taking all our parts and selling them to Bondo's gang.
Last night they stole all our Spiderspring Gears. The parts are in a bunch of crates they're guarding.
We need you to get our gears back, and show those Steelarm Pillagers they should pick on someone else.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take out those Steelarm Pillagers and get $1oa Spiderspring Gears back.
